## Common Issues

### Service not responding

1. Check the GCP Console: [Link](https://console.cloud.google.com/home/dashboard?project=${{ values.gcpProject }})
2. Review recent deployments in ArgoCD
3. Check logs in Cloud Logging

### High latency

1. Check resource utilization in GCP Monitoring
2. Review recent changes via `git log`
3. Scale up if needed via ArgoCD

